snippet: Lloyd Sam and Tim Cahill scored to lead the Red Bulls to a 2-1 victory over last-place D.C. United in Harrison, N.J.
abstract: New York Red Bulls defeat DC United, 2-1, to move into tie for first place.
lead_paragraph: Lloyd Sam and Tim Cahill scored to lead the Red Bulls to a 2-1 victory over last-place D.C. United in Harrison, N.J.

headline.main: Red Bulls Move Into a Tie for First
